## SpendWise Privacy Policy
SpendWise is an expense managing app developed by Richard Ejike. This privacy policy explains how we collect and use data in the app.

### Data Collection
SpendWise does not collect any personal information from users. However, we do collect non-personal data such as device information (e.g. device model, operating system version) and app usage data (e.g. which features are used most frequently) to improve the app and provide a better user experience.

We use third-party platforms to store this data securely, and we do not share this data with any third-party for marketing or advertising purposes.

### Data Protection Rights
Under this policy, users do not have any data protection rights as no personal information is collected. However, we take measures to ensure that all data is stored securely and is not accessible to unauthorized individuals.

### Updates to Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our data collection and use practices. Users will be notified of any significant changes to this policy through the app.

### Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at spendwise@richardejike.com.
